1283
01:37:41,655 --> 01:37:42,849
LYLE:
His hands were way up here.

1284
01:37:43,090 --> 01:37:45,888
KAZ: Missed him! He was safe!
LYLE: No way he could tag me. I was safe.

1285
01:37:46,093 --> 01:37:48,857
UMPIRE: Tag was good! Runner is out.
- We'll go get them this time.

1286
