Yeah, I touched the plate.

1292
01:38:05,312 --> 01:38:07,780
Of course you did. Game's over.

1293
01:38:08,015 --> 01:38:08,947
[ED SCOFFS]

1294
01:38:09,183 --> 01:38:11,117
Tie game, extra innings.
Let's go to the dugout.

1295
01:38:11,318 --> 01:38:13,183
- He was safe.
ED: What are you talking about?

1296
01:38:13,387 --> 01:38:16,083
The ump saw, I saw it, everybody saw it.
He's out. Come on--

1297
01:38:16,323 --> 01:38:19,224
I tagged him. I made the tag,
but I dropped the ball.

1298
01:38:19,426 --> 01:38:22,759
- He's safe. Run scores.
- I didn't see you drop the ball, catcher.

1299
01:38:23,864 --> 01:38:24,956
I know you didn't.

1300
01:38:25,199 --> 01:38:27,292
I did. Call it.

1301
